description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and self motivated technicians to join our cross site teams. The majority of rotations are at the Stoke Mandeville site however there are some rotations at Wycombe and Amersham Hospitals.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Pharmacy provides a comprehensive range of services to the Trust; outpatient / inpatient dispensing services, satellite units, aseptic services, medicines information, clinical services. Pharmacy has robots in the two main dispensaries and a large distribution robot.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The role involves rotation through dispensary, stores &amp; aseptic services.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You must be registered or be in the process of registering with the General Pharmaceutical Council to apply for this position . If you are a community technician considering swapping sectors, we would be happy to support you to move into hospital pharmacy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Greg Edwards Technician Team Manager Procurement &amp; Distribution 01296315280 or&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maxine Webb Chief Technician on 01296 316168&lt;/p&gt;
